  <thing id="rFirGenasi" name="Genasi, Fire" description="The heat of white flame burns in a fire genasi&apos;s heart.\n\nFire genasi are proud of their appearance, and generally strive for a look of simple elegance.  Specific traits that distinguish fire genasi from their human ancestors can include deep red or coal-black skin, red hair that moves on its own like waving flames, a voice that crackles like the sound of burning wood, warm or hot flesh, or fiery eyes that glow with flamelike intensity.\nFire genasi tend to be full of energy, high-strung, and quick to action.  They speak quickly and prefer action to discussion.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Monsters of Faerun, Races of Faerun" compset="Race">
